364
00:18:45,550 --> 00:18:46,990
The mortal world is truly wonderful.

365
00:18:49,040 --> 00:18:49,800
Look at that one.

366
00:18:50,070 --> 00:18:52,070
Smiling just like that Si Shulun.

367
00:18:52,850 --> 00:18:53,960
Go knock him out.

368
00:18:55,880 --> 00:18:56,750
