511
00:26:16,920 --> 00:26:17,480
Bring the seat of honor over.

512
00:26:17,920 --> 00:26:18,310
Quickly, quickly.

513
00:26:22,350 --> 00:26:24,590
I think the Sun Family is in dire straits now.

514
00:26:29,000 --> 00:26:29,590
Lord Si,

515
00:26:29,750 --> 00:26:31,110
