540
00:27:13,680 --> 00:27:14,790
Whoever dares to stop me,

541
00:27:15,550 --> 00:27:16,400
I

542
00:27:17,200 --> 00:27:18,000
don't mind

543
00:27:18,480 --> 00:27:19,940
